ff28a6d1a","tid":365733,"uid":86762,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T23:23:48.000Z","msg":"套嘢每一個學生都有自己嘅特點 故事<br />\n亦都冇忽略到其中一個人<br />\n我覺得呢點做得好好"},{"pid":"1c620f1791d0c1b4888625533d97dca06c0c7f89","tid":365733,"uid":360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T00:12:39.000Z","msg":"睇動畫結局睇幾多次喊幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尤其緒要親手殺死改變佢既恩師 真係好唔容易"},{"pid":"d9bf72f3b7bb9b70df4d5cc75421ebc89c9bfe41","tid":365733,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T00:57:43.000Z","msg":"唔夠魔人偵探好睇"},{"pid":"5f58049521417cf919d1b9d9e7df445e832868d0","tid":365733,"uid":37890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T03:55:13.000Z","msg":"睇漫畫結局咸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n動畫最尾我覺得應該用返ed1<br />\n前面好多日常劇情悶左少少<br />\n不過為左培養對角色既感情又唔cut得"},{"pid":"36b83730c32c3547ea63dc47db3f1985a185b48c","tid":365733,"uid":25520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:04:20.000Z","msg":"睇完都記唔到啲學生名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ddbfad5d338df85f9f1c51472835dc2a65fc6b","tid":365733,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:10:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔夠魔人偵探好睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n魔人真係少人識好多"},{"pid":"9bde4f0f595f309c2d4d617a2b0e9d0ed1644a89","tid":365733,"uid":5831,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T09:38:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完都記唔到啲學生名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然佢個個講 但我記名既得一隻手數哂 仲要唔係全名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小渚  芽野 磯貝 赤羽 正義 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小律計埋既多一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而兩個老師鳥間同bitch幾深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96dd73f40136cecbec54f9e7402260bca049d1df","tid":365733,"uid":63276,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:57:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇完都記唔到啲學生名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然佢個個講 但我記名既得一隻手數哂 仲要唔係全名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小渚  芽野 磯貝 赤羽 正義 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小律計埋既多一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而兩個老師鳥間同bitch幾深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n名都搞錯仲話好意思話深刻，重睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2b788b56e6f9ee40fac0df624efadcf0f0f0da","tid":365733,"uid":128089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:16:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇完都記唔到啲學生名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然佢個個講 但我記名既得一隻手數哂 仲要唔係全名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小渚  芽野 磯貝 赤羽 正義 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小律計埋既多一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而兩個老師鳥間同bitch幾深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n名都搞錯仲話好意思話深刻，重睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實鳥間都幾好聽，唔知佢打錯定點...<br />\n<br />\n有單野係同呢個譯名有關，<br />\n早期大陸個漢化組係譯錯咗烏間個名做鳥間<br />\n日文原文係烏間惟臣，當時的漢化組就以為呢個係「鸟」的正體字。<br />\n最後簡繁轉換就出咗個「鳥」字，又唔睇清楚兩個字唔同，最後錯咗好多集先俾人發現。<br />\n<br />\n呢件事就可以睇到用殘體字的CREATURE係幾咁柒。<br />\n當時貼吧有個POST係討論呢樣野，而當年貼吧係唔打得正體字，會自動簡繁轉換轉返做殘體字，<br />\n班友又要文盲，又要打唔到正體字，結果個討論亂到七彩，有興趣可以自己上暗殺教室貼吧度恥笑。"},{"pid":"825c6c0c0d3860841071ed9d14f635fa01f5d91f","tid":365733,"uid":58954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:31:26.000Z","msg":"啱啱翻睇緊 佳作以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作者刻畫人物性格真係好好 冇忽略任何一個角色<br />\n可以睇到角色嘅成長 啲日常都好窩心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c7024c2ce09a321e8187a8857cba4ad38ea9da","tid":365733,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T12:31:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔夠魔人偵探好睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n魔人真係少人識好多</blockquote><br />\n魔人偵探睇左3 次,真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}